title: PLAT 5 - LF Top Juggernaut Main and Tanky Supp Main for Dynamic Queue
body: I main Kindred Jungle, excellent in ganking and helping lanes snowball but I find Kindred very difficult to carry in late game with her short range and it is worsened when there is a lack of front liners in my team (ie: Juggernaut Top and Tanky Support). So I'm looking for these main players to dynamic queue with. Add me in game name QuiNSonG
